  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to see the correlation of polarization and the expresison of
      chemokine receptors of T help cells after allogeneic hematopoietic stem cell transplantation
      and clinical course graft-versus-host disease.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
